<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Webpage Analyzer</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Unfurl</h1>
        <p>I am analysing any website link you paste into that box, and giving you a response down below. That is the
            basis, of unfurl, you could say, unlock.</p>
        <form action="/analyze" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="urlInput">Enter URL:</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="urlInput" name="url" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-2" id="analyzeButton">Analyze</button>
        </form>
        <div class="mt-4">
            <div id="alertWorking" class="alert alert-info d-none" role="alert">
                Analysis is in progress...
            </div>
            <% if (result !==null) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                    <%= result %>
                </div>
                <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                    I have generated a screenshot of the webpage, down below.
                </div>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary mt-3">Go Back Home</a>
                <% } %>
        </div>
        <% if (screenshotPath) { %>
            <img src="<%= screenshotPath %>" class="img-fluid mt-4" alt="Screenshot">
            <% } %>
    </div>
